<section id="body">
  <img class="rightFloat" src="../media/MM_GW_003.jpg" mode="1" id="1001"/>
  <div id="dropdown">
  <p align="left">Dear Sir/Madam,</p>
  <p align="left">I am writing to thank you for&#xA0;<select id="q1"><option id="a1">your</option><option id="a2">a</option><option id="a3">my</option><option id="a4">(...)</option></select>&#xA0;fabulous series '&#xA0;<select id="q2"><option id="a5">A</option><option id="a6">An</option><option id="a7">The</option><option id="a8">(...)</option></select>&#xA0;Hundred Years of Radio'.</p>
  <p align="left"><select id="q3"><option id="a9">My</option><option id="a10">A</option><option id="a11">Your</option><option id="a12">(...)</option></select>&#xA0;whole family thoroughly enjoyed each of&#xA0;<select id="q4"><option id="a13">the</option><option id="a14">an</option><option id="a15">its</option><option id="a16">(...)</option></select>&#xA0;excellent broadcasts in&#xA0;<select id="q5"><option id="a17">the</option><option id="a18">a</option><option id="a19">its</option><option id="a20">(...)</option></select>&#xA0;series, so much so that on&#xA0;<select id="q6"><option id="a21">(...)</option><option id="a22">the</option><option id="a23">our</option><option id="a24">your</option></select>&#xA0;Thursday evenings we would all rush&#xA0;<select id="q7"><option id="a25">(...)</option><option id="a26">the</option><option id="a27">a</option><option id="a28">our</option></select>&#xA0;home expressly to listen to them.&#xA0;<select id="q8"><option id="a29">My</option><option id="a30">The</option><option id="a31">A</option><option id="a32">(...)</option></select>&#xA0;youngest son, who is only twelve, is not usually interested in&#xA0;<select id="q9"><option id="a33">(...)</option><option id="a34">the</option><option id="a35">a</option><option id="a36">our</option></select>&#xA0;radio programmes but even he enjoyed them. In fact, he found them invaluable as he has been doing&#xA0;<select id="q10"><option id="a37">a</option><option id="a38">the</option><option id="a39">our</option><option id="a40">(...)</option></select>&#xA0;project on&#xA0;<select id="q11"><option id="a41">the</option><option id="a42">a</option><option id="a43">an</option><option id="a44">(...)</option></select>&#xA0;history of radio at&#xA0;<select id="q12"><option id="a45">(...)</option><option id="a46">the</option><option id="a47">a</option><option id="a48">our</option></select>&#xA0;school.</p>
  <p align="left">I must say we particularly enjoyed&#xA0;<select id="q13"><option id="a49">the</option><option id="a50">a</option><option id="a51">your</option><option id="a52">(...)</option></select>&#xA0;fascinating narration by&#xA0;<select id="q14"><option id="a53">(...)</option><option id="a54">the</option><option id="a55">a</option><option id="a56">your</option></select>&#xA0;George Pickering and&#xA0;<select id="q15"><option id="a57">his</option><option id="a58">the</option><option id="a59">an</option><option id="a60">(...)</option></select>&#xA0;insightful comments, as well as all&#xA0;<select id="q16"><option id="a61">the</option><option id="a62">a</option><option id="a63">its</option><option id="a64">(...)</option></select>&#xA0; wonderful recordings from&#xA0;<select id="q17"><option id="a65">the</option><option id="a66">an</option><option id="a67">its</option><option id="a68">(...)</option></select>&#xA0;early days of radio.&#xA0;<select id="q18"><option id="a69">The</option><option id="a70">An</option><option id="a71">His</option><option id="a72">(...)</option></select>&#xA0;original and creative style of&#xA0;<select id="q19"><option id="a73">the</option><option id="a74">a</option><option id="a75">his</option><option id="a76">(...)</option></select>&#xA0;series was also extremely impressive.</p>
  <p align="left">We would very much like to know whether you are planning to air more stimulating programmes of this kind in&#xA0;<select id="q20"><option id="a77">the</option><option id="a78">a</option><option id="a79">our</option><option id="a80">(...)</option></select>&#xA0;future. If so, we would appreciate it if you could inform us in advance so that we do not miss them.</p>
  <p align="left">Thank you once again.</p>
  <p align="left">Yours faithfully,</p>
  <p align="left">Mrs M. Alty</p>
  <p align="left">
    <font size="2"/>
  </p>
